alizing opinion and what I have called \\\"rage rhetoric.\\\"\", \"from\": 2195, \"to\": 2307, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2208, \"end\": 2214, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.7848220878483383, \"rank\": 0.2725524115056278, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"opinion\", \"from\": 2260, \"to\": 2267}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"rage rhetoric\", \"from\": 2291, \"to\": 2305}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In France, such complaints are often criminal matters.\", \"from\": 2309, \"to\": 2363, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2312, \"end\": 2318, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kingdom_of_France\", \"score\": 0.5335495600518144, \"rank\": 0.5906282635441679, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kingdom_of_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kingdom_of_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"such complaints\", \"from\": 2320, \"to\": 2335}, {\"ngram\": \"criminal matters\", \"from\": 2346, \"to\": 2362}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In my new book, \\\"The Indispensable Right: Free Speech in an Age of Rage,\\\" I discuss the collapse of free speech rights in France as well as other European countries.\", \"from\": 2364, \"to\": 2529, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2486, \"end\": 2492, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kingdom_of_France\", \"score\": 0.5335495600518144, \"rank\": 0.5906282635441679, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kingdom_of_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kingdom_of_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my new book\", \"from\": 2367, \"to\": 2378}, {\"ngram\": \"Free Speech\", \"from\": 2406, \"to\": 2417}, {\"ngram\": \"an Age\", \"from\": 2421, \"to\": 2427}, {\"ngram\": \"Rage\", \"from\": 2431, \"to\": 2435}, {\"ngram\"